org.tiledreader

Class TiledWangTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tiledreader.TiledWangTile

  • public class TiledWangTile
extends java.lang.Object

    A TiledWangTile represents a Wang tile. It corresponds to a <wangtile> tag in a Tiled XML file.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Concrete Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      TiledWangColor getBottomColor()
      Returns this Wang tile's color on its bottom edge, or null if there is none.

      Returns this Wang tile's color at its bottom left corner, or null if there is none.

      Returns this Wang tile's color on its left edge, or null if there is none.
